I have never seen a kit for this but I know there is a company  
remaking the engine tin in fibreglass.

http://www.creativecarcraft.com/notforbug.htm

You would still need a converted engine bearer bar  and possibly a  
68-79 oil pump cover plate to bolt the bearer bar up to it.



